snippet.title: Amber Heard Loses 20 Lbs From Stress
snippet.description:
Amber Heard has reportedly lost 20 pounds due to stress, as court proceedings with Johnny Depp have been postponed until next month. The Danish Girl actress was scheduled to fly to London for a costume fitting this week, but sources say she never left LA, after producers cancelled the booking, fearing shed dropped too much weight.
Kim Kardashian had claimed that Taylor Swift "approved" of the song 'Famous' by hubby Kanye West where he refers to Taylor as the 'b' word. However, Taylor has denied the claims, saying that the first time she heard it was when the song was first released and that she felt "humiliated".
Dwayne The Rock Johnson hasn't eaten candy since 1989.
That's nearly 30 years since he's eaten a sugary treat.  Jimmy Fallon tried to temp Dwayne to break his ban with an array of candies on The Tonight Show, and The Rock finally caved in!Christina Grimmie has been laid to rest in her home state of New Jersey, one week after her tragic death. The Voice star, who was shot and killed while signing autographs at her concert in Orlando, was remembered during a private funeral with close friends and family. The service was paid for by Christinas mentor on The Voice, Adam Levine, who paid an emotional tribute to her following her tragic death.

snippet.title: amberlynn reid is... something else...
snippet.description:
So if you’ve never heard of Amberlynn Reid you should count yourself lucky. Our queen Amberlynnstarted as a weight loss channel almost a decade ago and well… you tell me how that’s going. Nowadays, Amberlynn Reid no longer identifies her channel as a weight loss one but she’s more of a daily vlogger -- but you’d be wrong to think she’s out here shooting some David Dobrik style wild ass vlogs. Unlike everyone else, Amberlynn changed up the whole vlogging game by making it super boring. Now, if you’re new to Amberlynn Reid’s channel, you’d notice how she’s always getting hate bombed and all her “fans” seem to be just reading her to filth in the comments all the time. Amberlynn Reid is such a notorious liar she made like a 20-minute video confessing to all the lies she’s said. Amberlynn Reid has lied about some serious stuff but since this isn’t a deep dive, I’ll just stick to the basic stuff but if you do want a deep dive into the history of Amberlynn Reid and the detail about all the stuff she’s done please leave a comment letting me know. Now, let me introduce you to a crucial character in our story: Becky. Ms. Becky is Amberlynn Reid’s girlfriend. Or should I say WAS -- but we’ll get into that later. So here’s the thing, Amberlynn started talking to Becky the second she broke up with her other ex, Destiny. Keep that in mind cuz it’s gonna come up. So, almost immediately, Becky and Amberlynn Reid move in together. Now, this is when we start seeing Becky be dragged down by Amber and also fall into the same bad eating habits as her. You can see how Becky gains weight over time throughout this relationship. You can also see Becky try to help Amber by telling her to eat healthier and encouraging her to exercise more but I guess Amber had more influence on Becky’s lifestyle than Becky did on Amber’s. You can also start seeing how Becky enables Amber by walking the dogs herself, by taking Amber to eat out every day, or by covering up for her when she’s caught in lies. During all this, you can also see Amber does not really appreciate just how much Becky does for her. Buttt things take a turn...

snippet.title: The Way They Were: Amber Heard and Johnny Depp's Relationship Timeline
snippet.description: As quickly as Amber Heard and Johnny Depp burned bright, they just as speedily split up. Although their marriage lasted just 15 months, the battle in courts and in the court of public opinion continued.  MORE: The oddest celebrity couples of all time!   The bodaciously beautiful people met on the sun-soaked set of The Rum Diary. Their cinematic chemistry was as hot as the Cuban locale where the flick was filmed. Depp had previously been partnered with French actress Vanessa Paradis for 14 years, and they had two children together — Lily-Rose Depp and John Christopher Depp III.  MORE: Celebrity couples with the best love stories!  Headline-grabbing rumors about the new couple were everywhere. They had a fierce and fiery marriage. From the moment they met, through their contentious divorce proceedings and legal entanglements that still ensnarl both celebrities, we present the definitive chronicle of the whirlwind romance and equally as swift demise that was Amber Heard and Johnny Depp.
